In earlier version, we use JsonObject for better readability. Now we focus on performance, so I intend to use grpc-java and protobuf-java ( After https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/3123 confirmed by grpc-team ).  cc @ascrutae 
[Updated] https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/3123 confirmed, **grpc-java 1.4.0 is still 1.6 compatibility**.

And collector should provide a HTTP service to lookup the gprc services listening port. The segment receive service will be deprecated and removed. cc @pengys5
